Evidence: Task 4 明确要求前端权限值使用小写并以此测试，[plan#L523](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-24-frontend-role-aware-plan.md#L523) [plan#L464](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-24-frontend-role-aware-plan.md#L464)。但设计路由契约仍写成大写 `['USE_AI_CHAT']` / `['MANAGE_SCHOOLS']`，[design#L399](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-23-frontend-role-aware-redesign-design.md#L399) [design#L402](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-23-frontend-role-aware-redesign-design.md#L402)；Task 12 也继续用 `hasPermission('USE_AI_CHAT')`，[plan#L846](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-24-frontend-role-aware-plan.md#L846)。  
Impact: 路由守卫、AI 浮窗、学校管理页权限判断会出现整片误判，F-06 仍未真正闭环。  
Suggested action: 统一成一套可执行契约，建议全前端都使用后端 enum value 的小写字符串；同时补充“权限命中/不命中”入口级路由测试。

`R2-02 | HIGH | design-concern`  
Evidence: Task 2b 的动机写的是支撑通知铃 badge、ActivityFeed、校长 KPI，[plan#L277](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-24-frontend-role-aware-plan.md#L277)。设计文档要求通知中心有未读 badge、下拉分 tab，且“校长看全校，教师看自己相关”，[design#L106](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-23-frontend-role-aware-redesign-design.md#L106) [design#L503](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-23-frontend-role-aware-redesign-design.md#L503)。但计划中的 API 只返回 `id/status/channel/created_at`，[plan#L343](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-24-frontend-role-aware-plan.md#L343)；Task 8 仍写“暂无通知”占位，[plan#L700](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-24-frontend-role-aware-plan.md#L700)；Task 11 的 ActivityFeed 也还是占位数据，[plan#L796](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-24-frontend-role-aware-plan.md#L796)。  
Impact: F-01 虽新增了后端任务，但前后端契约仍不足以完成目标 UX，通知铃、动态流、KPI 都无法真正接上。  
Suggested action: 先定义结构化响应字段，如 `kind/title/summary/unread/text/type/target_scope_match`，再把 NotificationBell 和 ActivityFeed 接入纳入同一批次，或明确整体延期。

