Evidence: Dashboard Summary 的所谓“角色分组测试”仍然只做弱断言：principal 只校验类型/字段存在，[plan#L145](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-24-frontend-role-aware-plan.md#L145)；grade_leader 只断言 `>= 0`，[plan#L171](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-24-frontend-role-aware-plan.md#L171)；homeroom_teacher 只断言 key 存在，[plan#L179](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-24-frontend-role-aware-plan.md#L179)。  
